Abengoa Buys Call Options on 1.75 Million Shares at 30.37 Euros Apiece

-- B y   E m m a   R o s s - T h o m a s
-- 
2011-05-16T07:07:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-16/abengoa-buys-call-options-on-1-75-million-shares-at-30-37-euros-apiece.html
Abengoa SA (ABG)  said it bought call
options on 1.75 million company shares with an execution price
of 30.37 euros per share. The transaction is related to the
issue of 250 million euros of convertible bonds in February 2010
that mature in February 2017, the company said in a regulatory
filing today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Emma Ross-Thomas at 
 erossthomas@bloomberg.net  